WEBVTT

1
00:04:08.310 --> 00:04:09.990 
谢谢  母亲  讲到这儿就行了
Thank you, Mother. That's enough.

2
00:04:09.990 --> 00:04:10.860 
爸爸
Papa.

3
00:04:10.860 --> 00:04:13.130 
谁都不准越过环礁
No one goes outside the reef.

4
00:04:13.130 --> 00:04:16.410 
这里很安全  世上没有黑暗势力
We are safe here. There is no darkness.

5
00:04:16.410 --> 00:04:18.280 
