- There's no monsters, no monsters. - It's the darkness!

8
00:04:25.010 --> 00:04:28.890 
不  环礁外只有风暴和汹涌的大海
No, there is nothing beyond our reef, but storms and rough seas.

9
00:04:28.900 --> 00:04:29.980 
我要吐了
I'm gonna throw up.

10
00:04:29.980 --> 00:04:32.780 
只要我们大家都待在这座岛上
As long as we stay on our very safe island...

11
00:04:32.780 --> 00:04:33.820 
就会很安全
we'll be fine.

12
00:04:33.820 --> 00:04:35.290 
传说都是真的
The legends are true.

13
00:04:35.290 --> 00:04:37.210 
一定有人会扬帆远航的
Someone will have to go.

